threads.title: 820-01958 draws 5v not coming up
threads.message:
The board is very clean 👌 no corrosion.
PPBUS_G3H=12.26v pulsing to 11.16v
PP3V3_G3H= 3.3v pulsing to 2.8v.
The rest power rails not present, and no voltages on big coils around u7800.

threads.title: 820-01958 draws 5v not coming up
threads.message:
Check diode mode an all coils around U7800.
If nothing strange, do the same for big coils on the MLB.

Check U7800 (SYM 1 OF 4) LDO voltages.
